summary: A comfortable Riverwood home located on the shores of White River. Complete with all the amenities and full NavMesh. Live quietly as Riverwood\'s watchful guardian.
descriptionHtml:
-DESCRIPTION-

A simple mod that places a carefully crafted and modestly furnished home on the edge of Riverwood. Complete with all your crafting needs, storage, mannequin, and scenic views. A perfect place for your Dragonborn to relax. Great for new players/characters, but is perfect for your longest played character as well. Enjoy.

If you like this mod, comment, vote, endorse, and check out my other mods.
